1. *Idemo* svi zajedno. (Let's all go together.)
2. Reci mi kad *idemo*. (Tell me when we are going.)
3. *Idemo* na večeru. (Let's go for dinner.)
4. *Idem* u šetnju. (I'm going for a walk.)
5. Možeš li da me pozoveš kad *idemo*? (Can you call me when we are going?)
6. *Idemo* u bioskop. (Let's go to the movies.)
7. Nismo još odlučili gde ćemo *ići*. (We haven't decided yet where we will go.)
8. *Idem* malo da prošetam. (I'm going to take a little walk.)
9. *Idemo* do grada. (Let's go to the city.)
10.Kad *idemo* na more? (When are we going to the sea?)